  "title": "Project Sales Lead (TRAVELING OPPORTUNITIES & COACHING PROVIDED)",
  "description": "<p>You’re driven, creative, and ready to make an impact — you just need the right opportunity.</p><p><strong>We bring the platform, training, and mentorship. You bring the energy and ambition.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><em>Who We Are</em></p><p><br />We’re a fast-moving marketing team based in Singapore 🇸🇬, turning bold ideas into standout campaigns for meaningful brands. From the first spark to the final spotlight, we make ideas happen — and we have fun doing it.</p><p><br /></p><p><em>What You’ll Be Doing</em></p><p><br />This role puts you right in the action. You’ll gain real-world marketing experience by working on live campaigns and events, not just watching from the sidelines.</p><p><br /></p><p><em>Your day-to-day will include:</em></p><ul><li>Supporting exciting marketing campaigns and live brand events</li><li>Working closely with different teams to bring projects to life</li><li>Getting hands-on with campaign execution, direct marketing, and client interactions</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br /><em>What You’ll Gain (and Why You’ll Love It)</em></p><ul><li><u>Learn by Doing</u><br />We believe the best way to grow is hands-on. You’ll receive personalised training and mentorship that builds real skills fast.</li><li><u>A Career, Not Just a Job</u><br />This role is designed as a launchpad, with clear progression and opportunities to grow as you perform.</li><li><u>Real Growth, Real Skills</u><br />Build confidence, creativity, and communication skills while learning how campaigns actually work in the real world.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><em>Who This Is Perfect For</em></p><ul><li>Recent graduates ready to get started</li><li>Career switchers looking for something more dynamic</li><li>Curious, motivated people who want to learn and grow</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>No long experience lists required — just the right mindset.</p><p><br /></p><p>👉 Apply now and start a marketing career that’s anything but boring 🚀</p>",
